~ radio
if GameManager.get_day_phase() < 2:
	=> radio_untriggered
elif GameManager.get_day_phase() == 2:
	=> radio_title
elif GameManager.get_day_phase() <= 4:
	=> radio_options
else:
	=> radio_finished
=> END

~ radio_untriggered
收音机[#radio]: 看起来是一台普通的收音机
=> END

